    • Constructor Detail

      • Reservation

        public Reservation(Customer customer,
                   Tour tour,
                   double price)
        Three-argument constructor. Passengers variable is initialized as an arraylist. Vegetarians and non-eaters are set to zero. The newly created reservation is added to the list of reservations of assigned customer and tour.
        Parameters:
        customer - the object of a type Customer
        tour - the object of a type Tour
        price - the price of the reservation as a double
